20 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
21 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 22 O.S. 2021, Section 1175.8, is
22 amended to read as follows:
23 Section 1175.8. A. If the medical supervisor reports that the
24 person appears to have achieved competency after a finding of
